BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Invitation: D-Talent! Biweekly Group Learning Session_Team_2
DTSTART;TZID=GMT 标准时间:20260527T143000
DTEND;TZID=GMT 标准时间:20260527T153000
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Dear D Talent Team\,\n\n尊敬的D Talent团队，\n\n \n\nWe 
 are pleased to invite you to our upcoming Biweekly Group Learning Session.
  This session will provide an opportunity to review progress on the ongoin
 g training courses\, discuss usage of Coursera accounts\, and track the tr
 aining hours. It is also an opportunity to align on upcoming tasks and cou
 rse content.\n\n我们诚挚地邀请您参加即将举行的 双周学习
 会议。本次会议将为大家提供一个回顾正在进行的培训
 课程进展、讨论Coursera账户使用情况以及跟踪培训时长的
 机会，同时也是一个对接即将开展的任务和课程内容的
 平台。\n\n \n\n会议主持人：小组长\n\nMeeting Host：Group Lead
 er\n\n \n\nThe meeting will cover:\n\n会议内容包括：\n\n*	Review of
  Coursera account usage and training hours.\n\nCoursera账户使用情况
 和培训时长的回顾。\n\n*	Discussion of upcoming tasks and course c
 ontent.\n\n即将开展的任务和课程内容的讨论。\n\n*	Feedback 
 and suggestions for improving our learning initiatives.\n\n提供改进学
 习计划的反馈和建议。\n\n \n\nNo.\n\nSelected by Group\n\nTopics\
 n\nCategory\n\n1\n\n1\n\nEmployee Full Lifecycle Platform/员工全生命
 周期平台\n\nHR\n\n2\n\n1\n\nBuild BCZ‘s Own Digital Ecosystem/自有
 AI生态\n\nIT\n\n3\n\n2\n\nAI Best Parameter Recommendations/AI Best 参
 数推荐\n\nPPI\n\n4\n\n2\n\nAI Knowledge Assistant/AI 知识助手\n\nIT
 \n\n5\n\n3\n\nEquipment Full Lifecycle Platform/设备全生命周期平
 台\n\nMachine\n\n6\n\n3\n\nAI Safety Behavior Observation/AI 安全行为
 观察\n\nESH\n\n7\n\n4\n\nAI Product Anomaly Analysis/AI Recipe Auto Opti
 mization/AI 产品异常分析/AI配方自动化\n\nQuality/PPI\n\n8\n\n4\
 n\nQuality Issues - AI Smart Solutions/质量问题AI智能解决方案\n\
 nQuality\n\n \n\nLooking forward to seeing you there!\n\n期待与您共
 聚一堂！\n\n \n\nBest regards\,\n\nBCZ Digital Talent Team\n\n \n\n___
 __________________________________________________________________________
